> Everything in this mouthwatering collection comes from a Black-owned or Black-founded business. Try Mini Grahams and Vanilla Wafers from Partake, an allergy-friendly brand that partners with organizations to fight food insecurity. Sip on a cup of coffee brewed with BLK & Bold's Medium Roast—founded by two friends, it's a mission-driven company that donates 5% of its gross profits to nonprofits across the country. That's not all: This bundle also features snacks made with heirloom corn from PipCorn, uplifting tea from Steepers Only, and super flavorful seasoning blends from the husband-and-wife-run brand Station 1923.

Enjoy your @Partake Vanilla Wafers Minis{2}.

Try the @Partake Classic Grahams Minis{2} for a delicious treat.

Snack on the @PipCorn Mini Cheddar Cheese Balls{2} made with heirloom corn.

Savor the @PipCorn Cinnamon Twists{2} for a sweet and spicy snack.

Add flavor with @Station 1923 Creole Smoke Seasoning{1}.

Sweeten your dishes with @Station 1923 Brown Sugar{1}.

Brew a cup of @BLK and Bold Ground Coffee{1} for a rich, mission-driven coffee experience.

Relax with a cup of @Steepers Only Chamomile Lavender Tea{1}.

